ttps:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/n1-768x427.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/n1-1536x853.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/n1-140x79.jpg 140w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/n1.jpg 1500w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p phong c\u00e1ch v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng&nbsp;<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>M\u1ed7i phong c\u00e1ch n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c d\u00f2ng v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u v\u00e0 ki\u1ec3u d\u00e1ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m kh\u00e1c nhau nh\u1eb1m th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00fang tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a phong c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00f3. V\u00ed d\u1ee5: phong c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i \u01b0u ti\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u m\u1edbi nh\u01b0 g\u1ed7 c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p, k\u00ednh, th\u00e9p, inox,&#8230;; phong c\u00e1ch c\u1ed5 \u0111i\u1ec3n \u01b0u ti\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng g\u1ed7 t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean qu\u00fd hi\u1ebfm k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u00f9ng ph\u00e0o ch\u1ec9, h\u1ecda ti\u1ebft tinh x\u1ea3o; phong c\u00e1ch indochine l\u1ea1i s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean c\u00f3 t\u00ednh th\u00f4 m\u1ed9c nh\u01b0 m\u00e2y, tre, g\u1ed7, \u0111\u00e1,&#8230;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/14-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-10525\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/14-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/14-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/14-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/14-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/14.jpg 1500w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Ngo\u00e0i ra, m\u1ed7i kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng, sinh ho\u1ea1t s\u1ebd ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi t\u1eebng d\u00f2ng v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u ri\u00eang bi\u1ec7t. Do \u0111\u00f3 khi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf, KTS c\u1ea7n t\u1ec9 m\u1ec9 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn, ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p c\u00e1c d\u00f2ng v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u h\u00e0i h\u00f2a \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00fang c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt khi \u1edf m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 n\u00e2ng \u0111\u1ee1 khi k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nhau. V\u00ed d\u1ee5: ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch v\u00e0 b\u1ebfp l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng gian sinh ho\u1ea1t chung n\u00ean c\u1ea7n c\u00e1c v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u mang l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 g\u1ea7n g\u0169i nh\u01b0 g\u1ed7, \u0111\u00e1, k\u00ednh,&#8230;; ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 l\u00e0 n\u01a1i ri\u00eang t\u01b0, d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n n\u00ean c\u1ea7n c\u00e1c v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u mang t\u1edbi s\u1ef1 \u1ea5m \u00e1p, th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n nh\u01b0 g\u1ed7, v\u1ea3i n\u1ec9,&#8230;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>T\u01b0\u01a1ng quan h\u00f2a h\u1ee3p xung quanh&nbsp;<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>M\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng gian n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u d\u00f2ng v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u kh\u00e1c nhau, ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady khi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf th\u1ea5t ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o s\u1ef1 h\u00e0i h\u00f2a t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eeb m\u00e0u s\u1eafc, ki\u1ec3u d\u00e1ng t\u1edbi v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, s\u1ef1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng quan h\u00f2a h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i \u1edf trong kh\u00f4ng gian n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t m\u00e0 c\u00f2n li\u00ean quan c\u1ea3 t\u1edbi c\u1ea3nh quan, m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng xung quanh. V\u00ec v\u1eady, khi l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n xem x\u00e9t y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 mang t\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng h\u00e0i h\u00f2a nh\u1ea5t.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"819\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/9a10129538e3cdbd94f212-1-1024x819.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-10526\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/9a10129538e3cdbd94f212-1-1024x819.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/9a10129538e3cdbd94f212-1-300x240.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/9a10129538e3cdbd94f212-1-768x614.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/9a10129538e3cdbd94f212-1-1536x1229.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/9a10129538e3cdbd94f212-1.jpg 1500w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf v\u00e0 thi c\u00f4ng. Do \u0111\u00f3, l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00fang, \u0111\u1ee7 v\u00e0 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p ch\u00fang lo\u1ea1i v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u s\u1ebd gi\u00fap c\u00f4ng tr\u00ecnh n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t b\u1ec1n v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb9p h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>>> Xem th\u00eam: <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/thiet-ke-noi-that-hien-dai\/\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/thiet-ke-noi-that-hien-dai\/\" target=\"_blank\">Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft<\/a><\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>>> Xem th\u00eam: <a href=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/nguyen-tac-co-ban-trong-thiet-ke-noi-that-chung-cu\/\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/nguyen-tac-co-ban-trong-thiet-ke-noi-that-chung-cu\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Nguy\u00ean t\u1eafc c\u01a1 b